name: hyperliquid_dart
desc: Dart SDK for the Hyperliquid DEX.

name: bpsOfMaxSupply
desc: Basis points of max supply staked

name: AssetContext
desc: Asset context data (funding rate, open interest, prices).

name: AssetMetadata
desc: Asset metadata from the universe array.

name: onlyIsolated
desc: Whether only isolated margin is allowed.

name: szDecimals
desc: Number of decimal places for size.

name: BuilderFee
desc: Builder fee configuration for order placement.

name: feeRate
desc: Fee rate in tenths of a basis point (e.g. 10 = 1bp = 0.01%).

name: toWire
desc: Serialize to the wire format expected by Hyperliquid.

name: Candle
desc: Raw candle data from Hyperliquid API.

name: CandleIntervals
desc: Candle interval strings accepted by the Hyperliquid API.

name: durationSeconds
desc: Map interval string to approximate duration in seconds.

name: ExchangeClient
desc:
Client for placing orders, cancelling orders, updating leverage, and other
write operations on the Hyperliquid exchange.

name: batchModify
desc: Modify multiple orders in a single atomic request.

name: cancelOrders
desc: Cancel one or more orders by their order IDs.

name: cancelOrdersByCloid
desc: Cancel orders by client order ID (cloid).

name: placeOrder
desc: Place one or more orders (perpetual futures or spot markets).

name: scheduleCancel
desc: Schedule automatic cancellation of all orders at a future time.

name: sendAsset
desc: Transfer assets between DEXs, addresses, and/or sub-accounts.

name: spotSend
desc: Send spot tokens to another address.

name: subAccountSpotTransfer
desc: Transfer spot tokens between sub-accounts (spot DEX only).

name: subAccountTransfer
desc: Transfer USDC between sub-accounts (perpetual DEX only).

name: twapOrder
desc: Place a TWAP (Time-Weighted Average Price) order.

name: updateIsolatedMargin
desc: Add or remove isolated margin for a position.

name: updateLeverage
desc: Update leverage for a perpetual asset.

name: usdClassTransfer
desc: Transfer USDC between spot and perpetual accounts.

name: usdSend
desc: Send USDC to another address (internal Hyperliquid transfer).

name: usdTransfer
desc: Transfer USDC to another address or sub-account.

name: vaultTransfer
desc: Transfer USDC to or from a vault.

name: withdraw
desc: Withdraw USDC to an external Ethereum address (via Arbitrum bridge).

name: ExchangeResponse
desc: Response from the Hyperliquid exchange endpoint.

name: errorMessage
desc: Extract error message from various response formats.

name: FollowerState
desc: Follower state for a specific user (structure TBD).

name: HttpTransport
desc: HTTP transport for making REST API calls to Hyperliquid.

name: exchangeUrl
desc: The base exchange URL for this transport.

name: infoUrl
desc: The base info URL for this transport.

name: postExchange
desc: Send a POST request to the Exchange endpoint.

name: postInfo
desc: Send a POST request to the Info endpoint.

name: HyperliquidApiException
desc: Exception thrown when the Hyperliquid API returns an error.

name: toString
desc: A string representation of this object.

name: arbitrumChainId
desc: Arbitrum One chain ID (used for user-signed actions).

name: domainName
desc: Domain name used in EIP-712 signing for L1 actions.

name: source
desc: Get the source string for the given network.

name: userSignedDomainName
desc: Domain name for user-signed actions (e.g. approveBuilderFee).

name: HyperliquidUrls
desc: Base URLs for Hyperliquid API endpoints.

name: exchangeUrl
desc: Get exchange URL for the given network.

name: infoUrl
desc: Get info URL for the given network.

name: wsUrl
desc: Get WebSocket URL for the given network.

name: InfoClient
desc: Client for querying Hyperliquid's Info endpoint (read-only).

name: allMids
desc: Fetch current mid prices for all perpetual assets.

name: candleSnapshot
desc: Fetch OHLCV candle snapshot for a specific time range.

name: candleSnapshotPaginated
desc: Fetch candle data with automatic pagination for large time ranges.

name: clearinghouseState
desc: Fetch a user's perpetuals clearinghouse state.

name: frontendOpenOrders
desc: Fetch a user's open orders including trigger/stop orders.

name: fundingHistory
desc: Fetch historical funding rates for a coin.

name: getSpotAssetId
desc: Get the asset ID for placing spot orders.

name: historicalOrders
desc: Fetch a user's historical orders (completed, cancelled, failed).

name: l2Book
desc: Fetch Level 2 orderbook snapshot for a coin.

name: leadingVaults
desc: Fetch all vaults managed by a specific vault leader.

name: maxBuilderFee
desc: Get the max approved builder fee for a user and HIP-3 builder.

name: metaAndAssetCtxs
desc: Fetch perpetuals metadata and asset contexts.

name: openOrders
desc: Fetch a user's open limit orders.

name: orderStatus
desc: Fetch order status by order ID.

name: perpDexs
desc: Get list of all HIP-3 builder-deployed perpetual DEXs.

name: portfolio
desc: Fetch user's portfolio with historical account value and PnL.

name: recentTrades
desc: Fetch recent trades for a coin (market tape).

name: spotClearinghouseState
desc: Fetch a user's spot token balances.

name: spotMetaAndAssetCtxs
desc: Fetch spot metadata combined with asset contexts.

name: tokenDetails
desc: Fetch detailed information for a specific token.

name: universeNames
desc: Fetch the asset universe names (convenience method).

name: userFees
desc: Get user's fee structure and trading costs.

name: userFills
desc: Fetch a user's recent trade fills (executions).

name: userFillsByTime
desc: Fetch a user's trade fills filtered by time range.

name: userFunding
desc: Fetch a user's funding payment history.

name: userNonFundingLedgerUpdates
desc: Get user's non-funding ledger updates (deposits, withdrawals, transfers).

name: userVaultEquities
desc: Fetch user's vault deposits across all vaults.

name: vaultDetails
desc: Fetch detailed information about a specific vault.

name: vaultSummaries
desc: Fetch summaries for all vaults on Hyperliquid.

name: LeadingVault
desc:
Vault information for vaults managed by a specific leader.
Note: The API currently only returns address and name fields.

name: nonce
desc: Get nonce (for withdrawals and some transfers)

name: usdc
desc: Get USDC amount (for deposit, withdraw, transfer operations)

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: Meta
desc: Meta response containing asset universe and collateral token.

name: MetaAndAssetCtxs
desc: Combined meta and asset contexts response.

name: assetCtxs
desc: Per-asset context data (same order as universe).

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: isPositionTpsl
desc: Whether this is a position TP/SL

name: isTrigger
desc: Whether this is a trigger order

name: order
desc: Order details if status is "order", null if "unknownOid"

name: OrderWire
desc: Wire format for a single order (field order is critical for msgpack).

name: toWire
desc: Serialize to the wire format with correct field ordering.

name: assetToFundingMultiplier
desc:
Map of asset to funding multiplier
Key: "dex:asset"
Value: Multiplier as string

name: assetToStreamingOiCap
desc:
Map of asset to streaming OI cap
Key: "dex:asset" (e.g., "xyz:AAPL")
Value: Cap as string (e.g., "25000000.0")

name: collateralToken
desc: Collateral token ID indicating which token is used as margin for this DEX

name: getCollateralSymbol
desc: Get collateral token symbol from ID

name: PortfolioPeriod
desc: Portfolio data for a specific time period.

name: PortfolioResponse
desc: Portfolio response with performance data across time periods.

name: periods
desc: Map of period name to period data

name: PrivateKeyWalletAdapter
desc: Signs EIP-712 typed data using a raw secp256k1 private key.

name: PrivateKeyWalletAdapter.new
desc: Create from a hex private key (with or without 0x prefix).

name: signTypedData
desc: Signs EIP-712 typed data and returns the full signature as a hex string.

name: asBool
desc: Convert to the boolean representation used by Hyperliquid (true = buy).

name: fromBool
desc: Create from boolean (true = buy, false = sell).

name: fromHyperliquid
desc: Create from Hyperliquid's string representation ('A' = sell, 'B' = buy).

name: values
desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: SignatureComponents
desc: Parsed signature components from an EIP-712 signature.

name: SpotMetaAndAssetCtxs
desc: Combined spot metadata and asset contexts

name: SubscriptionHandle
desc: A handle returned when subscribing, used to unsubscribe later.

name: value
desc: The string value sent to the Hyperliquid API.

desc: A constant List of the values in this enum, in order of their declaration.

name: endTime
desc: End timestamp (may be null if still running).

name: twapId
desc: TWAP ID (may be null for initial snapshot).

name: hash
desc: Note: hash will be "0x000...000" for TWAP fills.

name: twapId
desc: Associated TWAP ID (may be null in some WebSocket messages).

name: TwapWire
desc: TWAP (Time-Weighted Average Price) order wire format.

name: randomize
desc: Randomize execution timing (false = evenly spaced, true = randomized).

name: sz
desc: Total size to execute as string.

name: UserFees
desc: User fee structure and trading costs

name: nextTrialAvailableTimestamp
desc: Next trial available timestamp (null if no cooldown)

name: trial
desc: Fee trial info (null if not in trial)

name: userSpotAddRate
desc: User's spot add rate (spot maker rebate)

name: userSpotCrossRate
desc: User's spot cross rate (spot taker fee)

name: VaultDetails
desc: Detailed vault information including performance, followers, and configuration.

name: alwaysCloseOnWithdraw
desc: Whether to always close positions on withdrawal

name: VaultPortfolio
desc: Complete vault portfolio with performance metrics for different time periods.

name: VaultPortfolio.fromJson
desc:
Parse portfolio from API response which comes as an array of tuples.
Format: ["day", {...}, "week", {...}, "month", {...}, ...]

name: VaultRelationshipData
desc: Vault relationship data for parent/child vaults.

name: childAddresses
desc: Child vault addresses (only for parent vaults)

name: WalletAdapter
desc: Abstract wallet adapter interface for signing Hyperliquid transactions.

name: signTypedData
desc: Signs EIP-712 typed data and returns the full signature as a hex string.

name: userState
desc: User state with positions and margins

name: WebSocketClient
desc: High-level WebSocket client for subscribing to Hyperliquid real-time data.

name: subscribeAllMids
desc: Subscribe to real-time mid prices for all assets.

name: subscribeBbo
desc: Subscribe to best bid-offer updates for a coin.

name: subscribeL2Book
desc: Subscribe to real-time Level 2 orderbook updates.

name: subscribeOrderUpdates
desc: Subscribe to real-time order status updates.

name: subscribeRaw
desc: Generic raw subscription for any subscription type.

name: subscribeTrades
desc: Subscribe to real-time trade feed (market tape).

name: subscribeTwapStates
desc: Subscribe to current TWAP execution states for a user.

name: subscribeUserEvents
desc: Subscribe to user account event stream.

name: subscribeUserFills
desc: Subscribe to real-time user trade fills.

name: subscribeUserFundings
desc: Subscribe to real-time funding payment updates.

name: subscribeUserNonFundingLedgerUpdates
desc: Subscribe to user non-funding ledger updates (deposits, withdrawals, transfers).

name: subscribeUserTwapHistory
desc: Subscribe to user's TWAP execution history.

name: subscribeUserTwapSliceFills
desc: Subscribe to individual TWAP slice fills for a user.

name: subscribeWebData3
desc: Subscribe to webData3 aggregate user information.

name: WebSocketTransport
desc: WebSocket transport with automatic reconnection and message routing.

name: isConnected
desc: Whether the WebSocket is currently connected.

name: messages
desc: Stream of parsed JSON messages from the WebSocket.

name: send
desc: Send a JSON message through the WebSocket.

desc: Build EIP-712 typed data for spotSend action.

desc: Build EIP-712 typed data for usdClassTransfer.

desc: Build EIP-712 typed data for usdSend.

desc: Get the asset ID for a HIP-3 builder-deployed perpetual.

desc:
Get the asset ID for a regular perpetual by looking up its index in the
universe array.
